name: BURJO
description:
Burjo is a food stall from Indonesia, usually they sell like instant noodles, instant coffee, "bubur kacang ijo" which is BURJO , or "Bubur ketan hitam". there are different names for the place, some people called it "BURJO", some people called it "WARMINDO", then some people called it "WARKUN". usually people spend time with their friends, their family, their colleague, and also it can be place for dating!. and the price is moooore affordable! which is low-price... hope you'll like it!
